{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887400/extras/avatar.png?t=1729365194\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chicklet is a mind-bending puzzle game where a cute chick is trapped in a pixelated, multi-dimensional machine. Players must guide the chick through a series of intricate and innovative puzzles. Each level requires you to skillfully adjust pages, use various levers, and mechanisms to navigate the chick to the exit. As the game progresses, the puzzles become increasingly complex, truly testing your intellect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Design</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chicklet features retro-style pixel art, offering a nostalgic yet modern atmosphere. Each level is filled with carefully designed multi-dimensional pages and mechanisms. The visual aesthetic, combined with the challenge of the puzzles, provides players with a unique experience. The color palette and sound design complement the immersive atmosphere of the game.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2887400?t=1729365194","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887400/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1729365194","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887400/002ee054f8cd1d1fec83beab91875c8fd9aefd8c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729365194","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887400/002ee054f8cd1d1fec83beab91875c8fd9aefd8c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729365194","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3287880,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p